### 6.3 Interaction Patterns

**Auto-save:**
- Triggered 2 seconds after user stops typing
- Visual indicator: "Saving..." â†’ "Saved âœ“"
- No manual save button needed
- Works offline (syncs when reconnected)

**AI Generation Loading States:**
- "Generating scene..." with animated dots
- Estimated time: "This takes about 3 seconds"
- Cancel button if taking too long
- Error handling: "Generation failed. Try again?"

**Field Focus States:**
- Border highlights in section color
- Placeholder text fades
- Help text appears below field
- Character count shows for limited fields

**Scene Templates:**
- Hover shows template description
- Click applies template with animation
- Confirmation if overwriting existing content
- "Clear Template" option to reset

**Show Don't Tell Coach:**
- Expandable/collapsible panel
- Smooth slide animation
- Sticky at bottom of viewport
- "Apply" buttons for each suggestion
- "Apply All" for bulk changes

### 6.4 Responsive Behavior

**Desktop (>1024px):**
- Two-column layout where appropriate
- Side panel for scene list while editing
- Full width for text editor
- Floating action buttons

**Tablet (768px - 1024px):**
- Single column layout
- Collapsible scene list
- Touch-optimized buttons
- Swipe gestures for prev/next scene

**Mobile (<768px):**
- Stacked sections
- Simplified Movie Time fields
- Bottom sheet for templates
- Reduced AI features (core only)
- Quick mode recommended

### 6.5 Accessibility

**Keyboard Navigation:**
- Tab through all fields in logical order
- Enter to submit forms
- Esc to close modals/panels
- Arrow keys to navigate scenes
- Shortcuts: Ctrl+S save, Ctrl+G generate

**Screen Reader Support:**
- ARIA labels for all interactive elements
- Section headings properly structured
- Form field descriptions
- Status announcements for AI generation
- Skip links for long scenes

**Visual Accessibility:**
- Minimum contrast ratio 4.5:1
- Focus indicators on all interactive elements
- Color not sole indicator of status
- Resizable text without breaking layout
- High contrast mode support

