## 12. Future Enhancements (v2.0+)

### 12.1 Advanced AI Features

**Scene Continuity Checker:**
- AI analyzes scene transitions
- Flags jarring jumps or missing connective tissue
- Suggests transition sentences
- Checks for timeline consistency

**Character Consistency:**
- Tracks character mentions across scenes
- Flags out-of-character dialogue or actions
- Reminds about character arcs from Archetype Builder
- Suggests character development moments

**Pacing Analyzer:**
- Calculates scene length and intensity
- Visualizes pacing rhythm
- Identifies slow sections
- Recommends scene cuts or additions

**Dialogue Coach:**
- Specialized feedback for dialogue-heavy scenes
- Suggests subtext improvements
- Checks for distinct character voices
- Recommends beats and pauses

### 12.2 Collaboration Features

**Co-Writing Mode:**
- Multiple users can edit same story
- Scene assignments (you work on scene 3, I'll do scene 4)
- Comment threads on scenes
- Suggestion mode (like Google Docs)
- Version control and merge conflicts

**Feedback/Critique:**
- Share scenes with beta readers
- Inline comments and highlights
- Rating/voting on scene quality
- Consolidated feedback view

### 12.3 Enhanced Templates

**Custom Template Builder:**
- Users create and save their own templates
- Share templates with community
- Template marketplace (premium)
- Genre-specific template packs

**Scene Archetypes:**
- Beyond basic templates, full archetype scenes
- "The Training Montage"
- "The False Victory"
- "The Dark Night of the Soul"
- Based on Blake Snyder's Save the Cat beats

**Dynamic Templates:**
- Templates that adapt based on story context
- Pull character names automatically
- Reference prior scenes
- Adjust to story structure position

### 12.4 Export Enhancements

**Format-Specific Scene Rendering:**
- Screenplay format (scene headings, action, dialogue)
- Novel format (prose with chapter breaks)
- Outline format (beat sheet)
- Presentation format (slides per scene)

**Scene Filtering:**
- Export only selected scenes
- Export by structure act
- Export by character POV
- Export by emotional arc section

**Multimedia Scenes:**
- Attach images to scenes (mood boards)
- Audio notes or recordings
- Reference links
- Research document attachments

### 12.5 Learning Features

**Writing Tutorials:**
- In-app tutorials on Movie Time framework
- Show Don't Tell mini-course
- Sensory detail exercises
- Interactive writing challenges

**Progress Tracking:**
- Dashboard showing writing stats
- Scenes completed over time
- Show Don't Tell score trends
- Writing streak tracking

**Achievement System:**
- Badges for milestones
- "First Scene Complete"
- "Show Don't Tell Master" (10 scenes with 8+ score)
- "Marathon Writer" (20+ scenes in one story)
- Gamification to encourage completion

### 12.6 Professional Features

**Professional Export:**
- Industry-standard screenplay format
- Query letter integration
- Synopsis generation from scenes
- Logline suggestions

**Revision Tracking:**
- Full version history
- Compare scene versions
- Track changes over time
- Revert to previous versions

**Research Integration:**
- Link scenes to research notes
- Attach reference images
- Timeline consistency checker
- Fact verification suggestions

